WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:01.000
Decide quickly

2
00:00:01.100 --> 00:00:03.366
Do you want this old woman and the little blind man?

3
00:00:03.366 --> 00:00:04.333
Or a red star?

4
00:00:04.333 --> 00:00:05.933
Lin Lan, save Yaoyao

5
00:00:05.933 --> 00:00:08.666
Don't worry about me, as long as your family of three is fine

6
00:00:08.666 --> 00:00:10.600
I will die in peace.

7
00:00:10.600 --> 00:00:11.900
Shut up old woman

8
00:00:11.900 --> 00:00:13.533
Mom you beast

9
00:00:13.533 --> 00:00:15.033
I must kill you

10
00:00:15.333 --> 00:00:16.600
Kun, you are courting death

11
00:00:16.733 --> 00:00:18.000
See who dares to move

12
00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:20.066
Forget how big sister usually treats you

13
00:00:20.066 --> 00:00:21.766
Guys, don't listen to him

14
00:00:21.800 --> 00:00:23.500
Now we have two hostages in our hands

15
00:00:23.500 --> 00:00:24.333
They dare not do anything

16
00:00:24.333 --> 00:00:26.900
I know you are all bewitched by the quantity officer

17
00:00:26.933 --> 00:00:29.066
If you still recognize me as a big sister

18
00:00:29.200 --> 00:00:30.566
Just stand aside for me

19
00:00:30.600 --> 00:00:31.966
I can go on forever

20
00:00:32.333 --> 00:00:35.266
If anyone still insists on going one way to the dark

21
00:00:35.733 --> 00:00:37.300
Don't blame my men for being ruthless

22
00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:38.166
Brothers

23
00:00:38.333 --> 00:00:40.666
Think about what we've done before

24
00:00:40.966 --> 00:00:42.400
It's not enough to die ten times

25
00:00:42.766 --> 00:00:44.800
You won't let us go

26
00:00:44.800 --> 00:00:48.033
Only by following me can we have a way out

27
00:00:50.266 --> 00:00:51.400
We go together.

28
00:00:51.400 --> 00:00:52.700
Please give us a chance.

29
00:00:52.700 --> 00:00:53.800
Give us a chance.

30
00:00:53.933 --> 00:00:55.366
Mom don't come

31
00:00:55.566 --> 00:00:58.000
Come again if I give it to the old woman don't go

